safari.notes: Generates randomized signatures as per [draft-irtf-cfrg-det-sigs-with-noise](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/draft-irtf-cfrg-det-sigs-with-noise/), instead of deterministic signatures as per [RFC 8032](https://www.rfc-editor.org/rfc/rfc8032).
